title: Be the first to enjoy this New Energy Efficient Townhome in Trillium's
posting_body: ["Be the first to enjoy this New Energy Efficient Townhome in Trillium's gated community.", 'This unit features a spacious modern kitchen with ample natural light, stainless steel open floor-plan easy for entertaining, smart home appliances, a separate laundry room, additional storage, new light fixtures, patio area, new window treatments with impact glass.', 'Parking made easy with a 2-car garage and a spacious driveway for an additional car.', 'Get to know your neighbors while relaxing at the pet friendly community near the poolside cabanas or just walking around the two large lakes.', 'Located in a great area midway between Stuart and Port Salerno giving access to both places in minutes.', 'Enjoy Downtown Stuart, plenty of entertainment, beaches, shopping, golf, local parks and much more!', 'Please contact S&S Global for more information', 'show contact info']
